---
title: Beef Meatballs in Creamy Tomato Sauce with Basmati Rice and Pesto Drizzle
description: These Beef Meatballs in Creamy Tomato Sauce are a crowd pleaser and one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R48_W32_UK_F11798-4_Mainlow-e152d4f0.jpg
